      "parameters": {
        "description": "Use this tool to look up information about RAIS (Ritz AI Solutions) - the company, its services, founder, pricing philosophy, tech stack, use cases, and how a potential partnership would work. Call this tool whenever a user asks about what RAIS does, who they are, what solutions they offer, or how they can help a business.",
        "jsCode": "const knowledgeBase = `\n=== RAIS - RITZ AI SOLUTIONS KNOWLEDGE BASE ===\n\nCOMPANY OVERVIEW\n----------------\nName: RAIS (Ritz AI Solutions)\nWebsite: https://ritz-ai.solutions\nFounder: Kevin Ritz\nHeadquarters: Germany (EU-based, GDPR-compliant)\nStage: Early-stage AI automation agency (actively taking clients)\nMission: Help businesses grow and operate smarter through tailored AI automation solutions.\n\nFOUNDER\n-------\nKevin Ritz is a young entrepreneur and Entrepreneurship student at HS Koblenz (Germany).\nHe has hands-on experience in AI Quality Assurance (1und1/United Internet), n8n workflow automation, LLM integration, web development, and building AI-powered business tools.\nHis background combines technical depth with a strong business mindset \u2014 making RAIS a partner that understands both the tech AND the business side.\n\nWHAT RAIS DOES\n--------------\nRAIS builds custom AI automation solutions for small-to-medium businesses. The focus is on:\n1. AI Chat Agents / Customer Support Bots - 24/7 intelligent chat agents for websites that answer questions, qualify leads, and handle support \u2014 reducing workload while improving customer experience.\n2. Workflow Automation - Automating repetitive business processes using tools like n8n. Examples: lead management, email follow-ups, CRM updates, invoice processing, reporting.\n3. Lead Generation & Qualification - Automated systems that capture, score, and route leads to the right person at the right time.\n4. AI-Powered Data Pipelines - Connecting APIs, databases, and business tools so data flows automatically without manual input.\n5. Human-in-the-Loop Systems - Hybrid solutions where AI handles routine tasks and escalates to humans only when needed (e.g. complex support tickets via Telegram or email).\n\nTECH STACK\n----------\n- Workflow Automation: n8n (self-hosted, EU VPS)\n- AI Models: Google Gemini 2.0 Flash (efficient + capable), OpenAI GPT-4, Anthropic Claude\n- Hosting: Hostinger VPS (Frankfurt/EU), fully GDPR-compliant infrastructure\n- Frontend: HTML/CSS, custom chat widgets\n- Integrations: Google Sheets, Telegram, Email (SMTP), Webhooks, REST APIs, Airtable, Notion, Slack\n\nWHY RAIS?\n---------\n1. EU-Based & GDPR-First - All data stays in the EU. No shady data brokers. Privacy is built into every solution.\n2. Custom-Built, Not Cookie-Cutter - Every solution is tailored to the specific business. No bloated SaaS subscriptions.\n3. Affordable & Transparent Pricing - As a lean agency, RAIS offers enterprise-quality automation at startup-friendly rates.\n4. End-to-End Partnership - From strategy to deployment to ongoing support. RAIS handles the full lifecycle.\n5. Fast Iteration - Small team = fast decisions, quick builds, and agile adjustments based on feedback.\n\nUSE CASES & EXAMPLES\n--------------------\n- E-commerce store: AI chat agent answers product questions 24/7, reduces support tickets by 60%+\n- Consulting firm: Automated lead qualification funnel \u2014 prospects fill a form, AI scores them, top leads get instant follow-up email\n- Service business: AI agent books appointments, sends reminders, and escalates complex queries to staff via Telegram\n- SaaS company: Automated onboarding sequence \u2014 new users get personalized email flows based on their behavior\n- Real estate agency: AI agent pre-qualifies buyers/renters, collects key info, and notifies agents in real-time\n\nHOW A PARTNERSHIP WORKS\n-----------------------\nStep 1 - Discovery Call (Free): We understand your business, pain points, and goals. No commitment required.\nStep 2 - Custom Proposal: RAIS delivers a detailed plan with scope, timeline, and transparent pricing.\nStep 3 - Build & Test: We build the solution, test it thoroughly, and involve you in feedback loops.\nStep 4 - Deploy & Train: We deploy to your infrastructure and train your team on how to use/manage it.\nStep 5 - Ongoing Support: Optional retainer for maintenance, updates, and scaling as your business grows.\n\nPRICING PHILOSOPHY\n------------------\nRAIS believes in value-based pricing \u2014 you pay for results, not hours. Typical projects range from small automation fixes (a few hundred EUR) to full AI agent ecosystems (multi-thousand EUR). Every engagement starts with a free discovery call. No hidden fees.\n\nCONTACT & NEXT STEPS\n--------------------\nEmail: kevin@ritz-ai.solutions\nWebsite: https://ritz-ai.solutions\nTo get started: Send a message, describe your challenge, and Kevin will personally respond within 24 hours.\n\nFAQ\n---\nQ: Is my data safe with RAIS?\nA: Yes. All infrastructure is EU-hosted, GDPR-compliant, and your data is never shared with third parties.\n\nQ: Do I need technical knowledge to work with RAIS?\nA: No. RAIS handles all the technical complexity. You just describe what you want to achieve.\n\nQ: How long does a typical project take?\nA: Simple automations can be live within a week. Full AI agent systems typically take 2-4 weeks.\n\nQ: Can RAIS integrate with my existing tools?\nA: Almost certainly yes. RAIS works with 400+ integrations via n8n and custom API connections.\n\nQ: What makes RAIS different from big automation agencies?\nA: Direct access to the founder, no overhead bloat, faster delivery, lower cost, and a genuine investment in YOUR business success.\n`;\n\n// Simple keyword search through the knowledge base\nconst q = query.toLowerCase();\nreturn knowledgeBase;"
